Add the persistent AgentOS reactor lifecycle.

Upstream base: EdgeJS b1feaa2c2b36f443ee5d527161dd93f3ac1544d6.
This cannot live in the sysroot or generic POSIX provider: it owns the Node
environment and N-API/V8 lifecycle inside the root WASM module. The generated
ABI manifest and the production V8 reactor tests cover the exported state
machine and keep the port from drifting back to a command-style `_start`.

